						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 10 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold deposited with the temple servants <hi rend="italic">(patipādamūlattār)</hi> by one Paramaṉ Ādichachapiḍāri of Āyirattaḷi, for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Mahādēva at Tiruchchōṟṟuttuṟai with the daily supply of an <hi rend="italic">uḻakku</hi> of ghee as interest thereon. </p>						

